 your career may take you relationships forged during your mba experience with classmates faculty and alumni become lifelong bonds quick links stanford alumni association gsb alumni association alumni chapters worldwide lifelong learning alumni consulting team stanford gsb voices the gsb provides frameworks for decision making and business skills that are vital to leadership in the interconnected work i now oversee acumen fund which builds financially sustainable and scalable enterprises delivering affordable clean water health care and housing to the poor so that they can make their own decisions and solve their own problems not only did my gsb experience directly impact the thinking and structuring of our work but acumen fund continually benefits from and is inspired by stanford's initiatives insights students and larger alumni community jacqueline novogratz mba 1991 founder and ceo acumen fund inc more profiles stanford gsb alumni network stanford alumni become an integral part of your mba experience through active participation as mentors class speakers project resources and recruiters online alumni database available to alumni and mba students and searchable by name class year job industry function and more alumni mentor program local alumni are matched up one on one with a student based on career and recreational interests long distance link up this program matches students with alumni in cities across the nation and around the world student alumni dinner series mba student clubs organize small informal industry focused dinners at alumni homes international alumni gatherings executive challenge admissions faculty & research alumni recruiters & companies giving executive education news about the gsb copyright 2012 stanford graduate school of business site help terms of use & policies stanford university
